  },
  "description": "OPA decision logs for Trino access control (ADR 0020 + 0021 + 0022 + 0023). Each /allow, /rowFilters, /batchColumnMasks, and /batchMaskInput query Trino sends to OPA is logged as a single JSON line; this dashboard surfaces the deny rate, top denied users/operations, the active bundle revision the deciding pod is on, and the raw log stream for incident investigation.",
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "links": [],
  "panels": [
    {
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {"h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0},
      "id": 100,
      "panels": [],
      "title": "Summary",
      "type": "row"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {"type": "loki", "uid": "loki_datasource_01"},
      "description": "Total decisions OPA evaluated for Trino over the selected range (sum of allow + deny across all /allow, /rowFilters, /batchColumnMasks, and /batchMaskInput calls).",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {"mode": "thresholds"},
          "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [{"color": "green"}]},
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {"h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 1},
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["sum"], "fields": "", "values": false},
        "textMode": "auto"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "12.3.1",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {"type": "loki", "uid": "loki_datasource_01"},
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "sum(count_over_time({namespace=\"[% opa_namespace %]\", pod=~\"opa-trino-.*\"} |= `\"msg\":\"Decision Log\"` [$__range]))",
          "queryType": "instant",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Total Decisions",
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {"type": "loki", "uid": "loki_datasource_01"},
      "description": "OPA decisions that returned result:false over the selected range. Each one corresponds to a Trino query (or sub-operation) the policy refused.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {"mode": "thresholds"},
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {"color": "green"},
              {"color": "yellow", "value": 1},
              {"color": "red", "value": 50}
            ]
          },
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {"h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 6, "y": 1},
      "id": 2,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["sum"], "fields": "", "values": false},
        "textMode": "auto"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "12.3.1",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {"type": "loki", "uid": "loki_datasource_01"},
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "sum(count_over_time({namespace=\"[% opa_namespace %]\", pod=~\"opa-trino-.*\"} |= `\"msg\":\"Decision Log\"` |= `\"result\":false` [$__range]))",
          "queryType": "instant",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Denies",
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {"type": "loki", "uid": "loki_datasource_01"},
      "description": "Distinct usernames seen in OPA decision logs over the selected range. Service principals (superset_svc, voila_svc, openwebui_mcp_svc) appear here too — they pass via the is_system_identity carve-out rather than the approval-group gate.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {"mode": "thresholds"},
          "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [{"color": "blue"}]},
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {"h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 12, "y": 1},
      "id": 3,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false},
        "textMode": "auto"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "12.3.1",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {"type": "loki", "uid": "loki_datasource_01"},
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "count(sum by(user) (count_over_time({namespace=\"[% opa_namespace %]\", pod=~\"opa-trino-.*\"} |= `\"msg\":\"Decision Log\"` | json user=\"input.context.identity.user\" | user != `` [$__range])))",
          "queryType": "instant",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Unique Identities",
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {"type": "loki", "uid": "loki_datasource_01"},
      "description": "Active bundle revision each OPA replica is currently serving (one tile per pod). Sourced from OPA's Status Log -- emitted on every bundle poll cycle regardless of query traffic, so a quiet pod still reports its true state. Revision is the SPI's publishNow epoch_ms; identical values across tiles = replicas converged. Different values = one pod is lagging on its 5–10s poll cycle (real divergence; production tolerates up to ~10s by design).",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {"mode": "thresholds"},
          "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [{"color": "blue"}]},
          "mappings": [],
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {"h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 18, "y": 1},
      "id": 4,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "horizontal",
        "reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false},
        "textMode": "value_and_name"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "12.3.1",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {"type": "loki", "uid": "loki_datasource_01"},
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "max by(pod) (last_over_time({namespace=\"[% opa_namespace %]\", pod=~\"opa-trino-.*\"} |= `\"msg\":\"Status Log\"` | json | unwrap bundles_scout_users_active_revision [5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{pod}}",
          "queryType": "range",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Bundle Revision (per pod)",
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {"h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 5},
      "id": 101,
      "panels": [],
      "title": "Trends",
      "type": "row"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {"type": "loki", "uid": "loki_datasource_01"},
      "description": "Allow vs Deny rate over time. Stacked bars per $__interval bucket. A sudden cliff in allows or spike in denies usually means either the bundle just propagated a change that broke an in-flight workflow, or someone's identity / group membership rolled over.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"},
          "custom": {
            "axisCenteredZero": false,
            "axisColorMode": "text",
            "axisLabel": "",
            "axisPlacement": "auto",
            "barAlignment": 0,
            "drawStyle": "bars",
            "fillOpacity": 80,
            "gradientMode": "none",
            "hideFrom": {"legend": false, "tooltip": false, "viz": false},
            "lineInterpolation": "linear",
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "pointSize": 5,
            "scaleDistribution": {"type": "linear"},
            "showPoints": "auto",
            "spanNulls": false,
            "stacking": {"group": "A", "mode": "normal"},
            "thresholdsStyle": {"mode": "off"}
          },
          "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [{"color": "green"}]},
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "Allow"},
            "properties": [{"id": "color", "value": {"fixedColor": "green", "mode": "fixed"}}]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "Deny"},
            "properties": [{"id": "color", "value": {"fixedColor": "red", "mode": "fixed"}}]
          }
        ]
      },
      "gridPos": {"h": 9, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 6},
      "id": 5,
      "options": {
        "legend": {"calcs": ["sum"], "displayMode": "table", "placement": "right", "showLegend": true},
        "tooltip": {"mode": "multi", "sort": "desc"}
      },
      "pluginVersion": "12.3.1",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {"type": "loki", "uid": "loki_datasource_01"},
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "sum(count_over_time({namespace=\"[% opa_namespace %]\", pod=~\"opa-trino-.*\"} |= `\"msg\":\"Decision Log\"` |= `\"result\":true` [$__interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "Allow",
          "queryType": "range",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "datasource": {"type": "loki", "uid": "loki_datasource_01"},
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "sum(count_over_time({namespace=\"[% opa_namespace %]\", pod=~\"opa-trino-.*\"} |= `\"msg\":\"Decision Log\"` |= `\"result\":false` [$__interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "Deny",
          "queryType": "range",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Decisions Over Time",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {"h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 15},
      "id": 102,
      "panels": [],
      "title": "Breakdown",
      "type": "row"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {"type": "loki", "uid": "loki_datasource_01"},
      "description": "Users with the most denied decisions over the selected range. A user appearing here who shouldn't be denied is usually missing a scout-user group membership, has enabled=false on their Keycloak record, or — for end users impersonated through a service principal — has been removed from the realm entirely.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {"mode": "thresholds"},
          "custom": {
            "align": "auto",
            "cellOptions": {"type": "auto"},
            "inspect": false
          },
          "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [{"color": "red"}]}
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "Value"},
            "properties": [
              {"id": "displayName", "value": "Denies"},
              {"id": "custom.cellOptions", "value": {"mode": "gradient", "type": "gauge"}}
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "user"},
            "properties": [{"id": "displayName", "value": "User"}]
          }
        ]
      },
      "gridPos": {"h": 10, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 16},
      "id": 6,
      "options": {
        "cellHeight": "sm",
        "footer": {"countRows": false, "fields": "", "reducer": ["sum"], "show": false},
        "showHeader": true,
        "sortBy": [{"desc": true, "displayName": "Denies"}]
      },
      "pluginVersion": "12.3.1",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {"type": "loki", "uid": "loki_datasource_01"},
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "topk(20, sum by(user) (count_over_time({namespace=\"[% opa_namespace %]\", pod=~\"opa-trino-.*\"} |= `\"msg\":\"Decision Log\"` |= `\"result\":false` | json user=\"input.context.identity.user\" | user != `` [$__range])))",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true,
          "queryType": "instant",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Top Denied Users",
      "transformations": [
        {
          "id": "organize",
          "options": {
            "excludeByName": {"Time": true},
            "indexByName": {"user": 0, "Value": 1}
          }
        }
      ],
      "type": "table"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {"type": "loki", "uid": "loki_datasource_01"},
      "description": "Trino operations that were denied most often. ExecuteQuery / SelectFromColumns dominate normal traffic; spikes in CreateView, DropTable, or admin-style operations usually indicate a partner site experimenting with a permission they don't have. ImpersonateUser denies mean a non-service-principal client tried to set X-Trino-User — typically a misconfigured BI tool.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {"mode": "thresholds"},
          "custom": {
            "align": "auto",
            "cellOptions": {"type": "auto"},
            "inspect": false
          },
          "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [{"color": "red"}]}
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "Value"},
            "properties": [
              {"id": "displayName", "value": "Denies"},
              {"id": "custom.cellOptions", "value": {"mode": "gradient", "type": "gauge"}}
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "operation"},
            "properties": [{"id": "displayName", "value": "Operation"}]
          }
        ]
      },
      "gridPos": {"h": 10, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 16},
      "id": 7,
      "options": {
        "cellHeight": "sm",
        "footer": {"countRows": false, "fields": "", "reducer": ["sum"], "show": false},
        "showHeader": true,
        "sortBy": [{"desc": true, "displayName": "Denies"}]
      },
      "pluginVersion": "12.3.1",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {"type": "loki", "uid": "loki_datasource_01"},
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "topk(20, sum by(operation) (count_over_time({namespace=\"[% opa_namespace %]\", pod=~\"opa-trino-.*\"} |= `\"msg\":\"Decision Log\"` |= `\"result\":false` | json operation=\"input.action.operation\" | operation != `` [$__range])))",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true,
          "queryType": "instant",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Top Denied Operations",
      "transformations": [
        {
          "id": "organize",
          "options": {
            "excludeByName": {"Time": true},
            "indexByName": {"operation": 0, "Value": 1}
          }
        }
      ],
      "type": "table"
    },
    {
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {"h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 26},
      "id": 103,
      "panels": [],
      "title": "Logs",
      "type": "row"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {"type": "loki", "uid": "loki_datasource_01"},
      "description": "Recent OPA denies, reformatted to show the relevant fields inline (user, operation, decision_id). Click a row to expand the raw JSON, which includes input.action.resource for catalog/schema/table identification and the bundle revision the decision evaluated against.",
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {}, "overrides": []},
      "gridPos": {"h": 12, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 27},
      "id": 8,
      "options": {
        "dedupStrategy": "none",
